bhumit070/dotfiles.summary: The bhumit070/dotfiles repository has seen significant updates recently, with multiple push events occurring between November 5, 2024, and December 26, 2024. The primary focus of these updates has been on the brewfile, with adjustments made to aliases, including setting up trash-cli, and various updates to the brewfile itself.

bhumit070/video-encoder.summary: The bhumit070/video-encoder repository underwent notable changes on December 11, 2024, with two push events aimed at enhancing its functionality. These updates included modifications to the job file for filtering jobs by status and adjustments to run generate and push commands directly within a Docker container, along with the addition of job status and data to the job column.
